headline: KKR Releases 2026 Global Macro Outlook
summary: NEW YORK, December 17, 2025--KKR, a leading global investment firm, today released "High Grading," the 2026 Global Macro Outlook by Henry McVey, CIO of KKR’s Balance Sheet and Head of Global Macro and Asset Allocation (GMAA).
